>> How will communicating
with nature help us survive

00:00:12.670 --> 00:00:14.740 align:middle line:90%
a crisis?

00:00:14.740 --> 00:00:16.630 align:middle line:90%
Hi, I'm Bruce Lipton.

00:00:16.630 --> 00:00:19.480 align:middle line:10%
I'm your host for this
series, "Inner Evolution."

00:00:19.480 --> 00:00:22.396 align:middle line:90%
