00:22:18.110 --> 00:22:21.970 align:middle line:84%
A noble gas will hook up
with another noble gas

00:22:21.970 --> 00:22:24.160 align:middle line:84%
and create what
is conventionally

00:22:24.160 --> 00:22:25.960 align:middle line:90%
