00:22:37.990 --> 00:22:39.790 align:middle line:90%
And why is it an excitimer?

00:22:39.790 --> 00:22:44.620 align:middle line:84%
Why is it an excited coupling
when they come together?

00:22:44.620 --> 00:22:47.980 align:middle line:84%
And the answer, as we will
see in the nature of bringing

00:22:47.980 --> 00:22:53.200 align:middle line:84%
