in a laser tube.

00:22:58.990 --> 00:23:00.010 align:middle line:90%
And guess what?

00:23:00.010 --> 00:23:03.040 align:middle line:84%
All the gases and
lasers are noble gases.

00:23:03.040 --> 00:23:05.070 align:middle line:10%
How does a laser work?

00:23:05.070 --> 00:23:08.050 align:middle line:90%
It injects photons into the gas.

00:23:08.050 --> 00:23:11.170 align:middle line:84%
And as the noble gases
absorb these photons,

00:23:11.170 --> 00:23:12.280 align:middle line:90%
they get excited.

00:23:12.280 --> 00:23:14.620 align:middle line:84%
Then they couple with
other noble gases.

00:23:14.620 --> 00:23:17.050 align:middle line:84%
And then together, they
give off photons of light

00:23:17.050 --> 00:23:18.590 align:middle line:90%
as laser light.

00:23:18.590 --> 00:23:22.600 align:middle line:84%
Well, it also applies
to us as humans.

00:23:22.600 --> 00:23:26.170 align:middle line:84%
When we become enlightened
noble gases, guess what?

